          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C24L--line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">A</hi> Bard, grown desirous of saving his Pelf,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C24L--line-2" n="2">Built a House he was sure would hold none but himself;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C24L--line-3" n="3">This enrag'd God <hi rend="italics">Apollo</hi>, who <hi rend="italics">Mercury</hi> sent,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C24L--line-4" n="4">And bid him go ask what his Votary meant:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C24L--line-5" n="5">Some Foe to my Empire has been his Adviser,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C24L--line-6" n="6">'Tis of dreadful Portent when a Poet turns Miser!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C24L--line-7" n="7">Tell him, <hi rend="italics">Hermes</hi>, from me, tell that Subject of mine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C24L--line-8" n="8">I have sworn by the <hi rend="italics">Styx</hi>, to defeat his Design;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C24L--line-9" n="9">For wherever he lives, the <hi rend="italics">Muses</hi> shall reign,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y07C24L--line-10" n="10">And the <hi rend="italics">Muses</hi>, he knows, have a numerous Train.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
